{"tid":1576423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民調： 葉劉羅范湯家驊為行會最受支持成員之一 民陣為最受市民支持的政治團體","createTime":"2019-09-17T08:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T09:35:18.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"db5860490cf4d40d8fb53de0d48897194b3ba569","tid":1576423,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所調查發現，市民最支持的首5名行政會議非官守成員，<span style=\"color: red;\">分別為任志剛、葉劉淑儀，張宇人、羅范椒芬及湯家驊</span>，平均評分為30.8，是調查以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n中大新聞與傳播學院院長李立峯分析指出，由於香港市民不熟悉行政會議成員，多數依賴其本身知名度，而受逃犯條例影響，<span style=\"color: red;\">建制背景的行政會議成員分數大幅下跌</span>。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">民陣</span>在政治團體中最受市民支持，評分為51.2，<span style=\"color: red;\">其次為香港眾志、公民黨、民主黨及人民力量</span>；<span style=\"color: red;\">建制派的自由黨、新民黨、工聯會及民建聯的評分創歷來新低</span>。<br />\n<br />\n李立峯認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於在反修例運動中沒有扮演大台的位置，民陣在運動取得大量民意，得到過半數的市民支持</span>。<br />\n<br />\n研究所本月初以隨機抽樣電話訪問，成功訪問1046名18歲或以上操粵語的香港居民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2252356/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2252356%2F&d=ZtzEMfLxU%2BwdrFVc2rz1%2FzKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=e2b4728f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2252356/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b91c3634d0b5611a44771dfdf35dff0e433ff2b","tid":1576423,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應